a stunning light show\", \"from\": 641, \"to\": 662}, {\"ngram\": \"the eight sprinters\", \"from\": 670, \"to\": 689}, {\"ngram\": \"the stadium announcer\", \"from\": 722, \"to\": 743}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Having made their way to the track, the athletes were then forced to endure a wait in excess of three minutes before they were ordered to position themselves on the starting blocks.\", \"from\": 746, \"to\": 927, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"their way\", \"from\": 758, \"to\": 767}, {\"ngram\": \"the track\", \"from\": 771, \"to\": 780}, {\"ngram\": \"the athletes\", \"from\": 782, \"to\": 794}, {\"ngram\": \"a wait\", \"from\": 822, \"to\": 828}, {\"ngram\": \"excess\", \"from\": 832, \"to\": 838}, {\"ngram\": \"the starting blocks\", \"from\": 907, \"to\": 926}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Dramatic music was playing inside the Stade de France while the sprinters waited ahead of the start line, however, the delay was considered excessive by both commentators and fans.\", \"from\": 929, \"to\": 1109, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Dramatic music\", \"from\": 929, \"to\": 943}, {\"ngram\": \"the Stade de France\", \"from\": 963, \"to\": 982}, {\"ngram\": \"the sprinters\", \"from\": 989, \"to\": 1002}, {\"ngram\": \"the start line\", \"from\": 1019, \"to\": 1033}, {\"ngram\": \"the delay\", \"from\": 1044, \"to\": 1053}, {\"ngram\": \"both commentators\", \"from\": 1082, \"to\": 1099}, {\"ngram\": \"fans\", \"from\": 1104, \"to\": 1108}]}, {\"sentence\": \"https://t.co/Cy8lgFGbMMpic.twitter.com/MK78mTkuIe But it has since emerged that moments before the sprinters walked out from the backstage area for the 100m final, a person was tackled by security as they attempted to get on the track.\", \"from\": 1111, \"to\": 1347, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the sprinters\", \"from\": 1206, \"to\": 1219}, {\"ngram\": \"the backstage area\", \"from\": 1236, \"to\": 1254}, {\"ngram\": \"the 100m\", \"from\": 1259, \"to\": 1267}, {\"ngram\": \"a person\", \"from\": 1275, \"to\": 1283}, {\"ngram\": \"security\", \"from\": 1299, \"to\": 1307}, {\"ngram\": \"the track\", \"from\": 1336, \"to\": 1345}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The individual, who was wearing a T-shirt which read, 'free Palestine, free Ukraine' on the front, was led away by four members of security staff.\", \"from\": 1349, \"to\": 1495, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1409, \"end\": 1418, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/State_of_Palestine\", \"score\": 0.8367692097664583, \"rank\": 0.16676410004382478, \"text\": \"Palestine\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/State_of_Palestine\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/State_of_Palestine\"}, {\"begin\": 1425, \"end\": 1432, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ukraine_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.9591125886070194, \"rank\": 0.042620050072761546, \"text\": \"Ukraine\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ukraine_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ukraine_national_football_team\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The individual\", \"from\": 1349, \"to\": 1363}, {\"ngram\": \"a T-shirt\", \"from\": 1381, \"to\": 1390}, {\"ngram\": \"the front\", \"from\": 1437, \"to\": 1446}, {\"ngram\": \"four members\", \"from\": 1464, \"to\": 1476}, {\"ngram\": \"security staff\", \"from\": 1480, \"to\": 1494}]}, {\"sentence\": \"When it was pointed out that someone had attempted to gain access to the track before the start of the 100m final, Lyles said in his post-race press conference: 'Is that what we were waiting for?\", \"from\": 1497, \"to\": 1692, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1612, \"end\": 1617, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Trey_Lyles\", \"score\": 0.8683092800203749, \"rank\": 0.14940199940770896, \"text\": \"Lyles\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q3665646\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Trey_Lyles\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Trey_Lyles\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"someone\", \"from\": 1526, \"to\": 1533}, {\"ngram\": \"access\", \"from\": 1556, \"to\": 1562}, {\"ngram\": \"the track\", \"from\": 1566, \"to\": 1575}, {\"ngram\": \"the start\", \"from\": 1583, \"to\": 1592}, {\"ngram\": \"the 100m\", \"from\": 1596, \"to\": 1604}, {\"ngram\": \"his post-race press conference\", \"from\": 1626, \"to\": 1656}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'I did not see anybody try to get on the field.\", \"from\": 1694, \"to\": 1741, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"anybody\", \"from\": 1709, \"to\": 1716}, {\"ngram\": \"the field\", \"from\": 1731, \"to\": 1740}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But I was wondering what we were waiting for, not gonna lie.\", \"from\": 1742, \"to\": 1802, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"'But, in the meantime, the crowd were constantly getting more and more hyped.\", \"from\": 1804, \"to\": 1881, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the meantime\", \"from\": 1813, \"to\": 1825}, {\"ngram\": \"the crowd\", \"from\": 1827, \"to\": 1836}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It did not feel as if it was completely dead.'\", \"from\": 1882, \"to\": 1928, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Kerley, who was also in the press conference with Lyles, shrugged and added: 'We did not see nothing.'\", \"from\": 1930, \"to\": 2032, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1980, \"end\": 1985, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Trey_Lyles\", \"score\": 0.8683092800203749, \"rank\": 0.14940199940770896, \"text\": \"Lyles\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q3665646\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Trey_Lyles\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Trey_Lyles\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Kerley\", \"from\": 1930, \"to\": 1936}, {\"ngram\": \"the press conference\", \"from\": 1954, \"to\": 1974}, {\"ngram\": \"nothing\", \"from\": 2023, \"to\": 203